title: IFaxDocument::get_ScheduleType (faxcomex.h)
description: The IFaxDocument::get_ScheduleType property indicates when to schedule the fax job; for example, you can specify that the fax service send the fax immediately, at a specified time, or during a predefined discount period. (Get)
